? SurveyResultBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc.itrust.beans.SurveyResultBean

  • public class SurveyResultBean
extends java.lang.Object
    Bean to be used for survey results (search). Stores address information about a HCP in addition to their specialty, hospital, and averages from survey (results range from 1-5). This beans also contains a variable that stores the percent of office visits that satisfaction results are available.
